Nulaxy T Stand

Nulaxy T stand is upgraded version with long aluminum arm to help to provide you best viewing angle while using mobile phone or tablet.

Enjoy a comfortable, custom viewing angle and hands-free convenience with this Nulaxy Adjustable Cell Phone Stand for iPhone and Android. The sturdy, portable stand keeps your smartphone right where you want it. This cell phone stand support hands-free and raises your phone up and away from desktop clutter.

  • Wide Compatibility: Nulaxy Phone Stand is compatible with iPhone and Android devices (measuring between 4 and 8 inches).
  • Adjustable: A 45 tilt range and ergonomic height design give you a comfortable viewing angle so you dont need to twist and turn your neck all the time!
  • Sturdy Enough: Comes with heavy base, designed on a low center of gravity makes it stable.
  • Rubber Protection: With a fully covered silicone pad to protect your device from scratches and slide.
  • Hollow Design: The hollow size is 33mm, it allows you to charge your device easily, you can watch video or reading while charging.

How does Amazon calculate star ratings?
Amazon calculates a products star ratings based on a machine learned model instead of a raw data average. The model takes into account factors including the age of a rating, whether the ratings are from verified purchasers, and factors that establish reviewer trustworthiness.
